        "title": "feat(cron): surface fallback progress",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Stop model fallback from starting or continuing while the Gateway is draining for restart/shutdown.\n- Add queue pressure fields to model fallback observations and surface cron primary/fallback progress into detached task run status.\n- Thread cron task run ids through manual/isolated execution and document the production AI governance checklist.\n\n## Verification\n\n- PASS: `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`\n- PASS: `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/model-fallback.test.ts src/process/command-queue.test.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/run-executor.task-progress.test.ts` (3 shards, 111 tests)\n- PASS: `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.core.test.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core-test.tsbuildinfo`\n- PASS: `./node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/agents/model-fallback.ts src/agents/model-fallback.test.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/run-executor.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/run-executor.task-progress.test.ts src/cron/service/ops.ts src/cron/service/timer.ts src/gateway/server-cron.ts src/agents/model-fallback-observation.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/run.ts src/cron/service/state.ts src/process/command-queue.test.ts`\n- PASS: `git diff --check HEAD~1..HEAD`\n- PASS: `node scripts/docs-list.js`\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: Cron/background task status now receives primary model and fallback progress, including queue active/queued/draining causality; model fallback refuses to run while Gateway restart drain is active.\n\nReal environment tested: Local macOS source checkout at `/private/tmp/openclaw-pr-87343-rebase`, PR branch rebased/cherry-picked onto `upstream/main` at `7385c611fcf3e696d2d7bb171905ac33522aad8f`, pushed as PR head `af7757dd8a41f54a70013b2d706ad2d16b4febb1`.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`; `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/model-fallback.test.ts src/process/command-queue.test.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/run-executor.task-progress.test.ts`; `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.core.test.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core-test.tsbuildinfo`; targeted `oxfmt --check`; `git diff --check HEAD~1..HEAD`; `node scripts/docs-list.js`.\n\nEvidence after fix: Targeted tests passed with 3 Vitest shards and 111/111 tests, core test typecheck exited 0, targeted formatter exited 0, docs listing exited 0, and diff whitespace check exited 0.\n\nObserved result after fix: The cron task-progress test records primary and fallback status updates; model fallback drain tests throw `GatewayDrainingError` before starting or continuing fallback; queue observation fields report active/queued/draining counts.\n\nWhat was not tested: Full local `pnpm check:changed` and full GitHub CI were not run locally. After the latest push, GitHub reported this PR as `mergeable=true`; branch protection checks are still subject to the current GitHub workflow results.\n",
